French Original: Book one of our hand-picked doctors in under 2 minutes
Bosnian Translation: Zakažite termin kod naših pažljivo odabranih doktora za manje od 2 minute
Notes: English source - needs French then Bosnian

French Original: Connect with certified healthcare professionals for secure video consultations. Available 24/7 across Europe.
Bosnian Translation: Povežite se sa certificiranim zdravstvenim radnicima za sigurne video konsultacije. Dostupno 24/7 širom Evrope.

French Original: Connect with certified specialists across various medical fields. All our doctors are verified and highly rated by patients.
Bosnian Translation: Povežite se sa certificiranim specijalistima iz različitih medicinskih oblasti. Svi naši doktori su verificirani i visoko ocijenjeni od strane pacijenata.

French Original: Simple booking process—set if available doctors first
Bosnian Translation: Jednostavan proces rezervacije—prvo provjerite dostupne doktore

French Original: Browse our verified specialists and check their real-time availability. Filter by specialty language and rating.
Bosnian Translation: Pregledajte naše verificirane specijaliste i provjerite njihovu dostupnost u realnom vremenu. Filtrirajte prema specijalnosti jeziku i ocjeni.

French Original: Select an available time slot and complete your booking in under 2 minutes. Secure payment processing included.
Bosnian Translation: Odaberite dostupan termin i završite rezervaciju za manje od 2 minute. Uključena je sigurna obrada plaćanja.

French Original: Join your secure video consultation at the scheduled time. Get professional medical advice and prescriptions.
Bosnian Translation: Pridružite se vašoj sigurnoj video konsultaciji u zakazano vrijeme. Dobijte profesionalni medicinski savjet i recepte.

French Original: Your medical data is protected with the highest security standards and European privacy regulations.
Bosnian Translation: Vaši medicinski podaci su zaštićeni najvišim sigurnosnim standardima i evropskim propisima o privatnosti.

French Original: Access healthcare professionals around the clock including weekends and holidays.
Bosnian Translation: Pristupite zdravstvenim radnicima tokom cijelog dana uključujući vikende i praznike.

French Original: All our healthcare providers are licensed certified and regularly reviewed by our medical board.
Bosnian Translation: Svi naši pružaoci zdravstvenih usluga su licencirani certificirani i redovno revidirani od strane našeg medicinskog odbora.

French Original: Access consultations from any device - desktop tablet or smartphone with seamless experience.
Bosnian Translation: Pristupite konsultacijama sa bilo kojeg uređaja - desktop tablet ili pametnog telefona sa besprijekornim iskustvom.

French Original: Keep track of your consultation history prescriptions and medical records in one secure place.
Bosnian Translation: Pratite svoju historiju konsultacija recepte i medicinsku dokumentaciju na jednom sigurnom mjestu.

French Original: Experience healthcare the modern way with our comprehensive telemedicine platform.
Bosnian Translation: Iskusite zdravstvenu njegu na moderan način sa našom sveobuhvatnom telemedicinskom platformom.

French Original: Join thousands of satisfied patients who have experienced quality healthcare through our platform.
Bosnian Translation: Pridružite se hiljadama zadovoljnih pacijenata koji su iskusili kvalitetnu zdravstvenu njegu kroz našu platformu.

French Original: Transparent pricing with no hidden fees. Choose the plan that works best for you.
Bosnian Translation: Transparentne cijene bez skrivenih naknada. Odaberite plan koji vam najbolje odgovara.
23% uštede u odnosu na mjesečni plan

French Original: Skip the waiting room. Book now.
Join thousands of patients who have already experienced the future of healthcare. Get started with your first consultation today.
Bosnian Translation: Pridružite se hiljadama pacijenata koji su već iskusili budućnost zdravstvene njege. Započnite sa vašom prvom konsultacijom danas.

French Original: No available slots for this date
Bosnian Translation: Nema dostupnih termina za ovaj datum

French Original: The page you are looking for does not exist.
An error occurred. Please try again.
Bosnian Translation: Došlo je do greške. Molimo pokušajte ponovo.

French Original: Password must be at least 8 characters
